"```sql\nSELECT district.district_id\nFROM loan\nJOIN account ON loan.account_id = account.account_id\nJOIN district ON account.district_id = district.district_id\nWHERE loan.date = '1994-08-25';\n```\n\nThis SQL query retrieves the `district_id` of the branch where the account associated with a loan approved on August 25, 1994, was opened. It joins the `loan`, `account`, and `district` tables using the foreign key relationships defined in the schema."